</node>
<node id="&quot;RÉFÉRENDUM D'INITIATIVE CITOYENNE (RIC)&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The Référendum d'initiative citoyenne (RIC) is proposed as a means for citizens to initiate referendums, reflecting a demand for greater direct democracy."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-7ab3715b4d98c886a01a39de25141116</data>
  <data key="d3">"RÉFÉRENDUM D'INITIATIVE CITOYENNE (RIC)"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SMIC&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"SERVICEPUBLIC"</data>
  <data key="d1">"SMIC (Salaire Minimum Interprofessionnel de Croissance) is the minimum wage in France, the proposal suggests its increase to improve citizens' economic situation."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-7ab3715b4d98c886a01a39de25141116</data>
  <data key="d3">"SMIC"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ISF&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TYPEIMPOT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"ISF (Impôt de Solidarité sur la Fortune) is a tax on large fortunes, which is suggested to be increased significantly for wealth redistribution."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-7ab3715b4d98c886a01a39de25141116</data>
  <data key="d3">"ISF"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BRUXELLES (UE)&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ACTEURINSTITUTIONNEL"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bruxelles refers to the European Union's governing body, and the text expresses a desire for national sovereignty away from its influence."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-7ab3715b4d98c886a01a39de25141116</data>
  <data key="d3">"BRUXELLES (UE)"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LOI DU 3 JANVIER 1973&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"REFORMEDEMOCRATIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The law of January 3, 1973 is criticized for causing national debt issues, with a call to repeal it as it is deemed illegitimate by the citizens."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-7ab3715b4d98c886a01a39de25141116</data>
  <data key="d3">"LOI DU 3 JANVIER 1973"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PRÉCARITÉ&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"THEMATIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Précarité addresses the issue of job insecurity faced by workers in CDD (Contrat à Durée Déterminée) and interim positions, which citizens wish to mitigate."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-7ab3715b4d98c886a01a39de25141116</data>
  <data key="d3">"PRÉCARITÉ"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;RETRAITE DES PRÉSIDENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The proposal suggests ending lifetime pensions for former presidents, indicating a desire for accountability and economic justice."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-7ab3715b4d98c886a01a39de25141116</data>
  <data key="d3">"RETRAITE DES PRÉSIDENTS"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;POLLUTION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"THEMATIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Pollution relates to environmental concerns, with a proposal to heavily tax significant polluters such as companies and means of transport like ships and planes."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-7ab3715b4d98c886a01a39de25141116</data>
  <data key="d3">"POLLUTION"</data>
